text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to avoid getting bunions?
text.Response A: Some ways to avoid getting bunions include wearing comfortable shoes with proper support, avoiding high heels or shoes that are too tight, stretching exercises to improve foot flexibility, and maintaining a healthy weight to reduce pressure on the feet.
text.Response B: We recommend avoiding tight shoes, and regularly stretching your feet.

Prompt

Can you tell me how to avoid getting bunions?

Response A

Some ways to avoid getting bunions include wearing comfortable shoes with proper support, avoiding high heels or shoes that are too tight, stretching exercises to improve foot flexibility, and maintaining a healthy weight to reduce pressure on the feet.

Response B

We recommend avoiding tight shoes, and regularly stretching your feet.
